<cell id="cell-0"><cell_type>markdown</cell_type># Lab 3.8 — Ragas
Primary path: the `ragas` library with an Anthropic-backed judge + Voyage embeddings.
Teaching cells at the end unpack two metrics by hand so you see the math.
The exported `evaluate()` is what 3.10 (gate) and Capstone M2 import — ragas underneath.
Cost: ~$0.45 for the full 20-Q run (ragas runs more judge calls than a hand-rolled
harness — that is the tradeoff for battle-tested prompts).</cell id="cell-0">
